      "chapterNumber": 1,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 1:29",
      "text": "ܕܠܐ ܢܫܬܒܗܪ ܟܠ ܒܤܪ ܩܕܡܘܗܝ ܀",
